Jack Nance https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Nance 0 Marvin John Nance (December 21, 1943 – December 30, 1996) was an American actor of stage and screen.He was known for his work with director David Lynch, particularly for his starring roles in Eraserhead (1977) and Twin Peaks (1990–1991).
